  <brief_title>Study to Compare QVM149 and Free Triple Combination of Salmeterol/Fluticasone + Tiotropium</brief_title>
  <acronym>ARGON</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Partially-blinded, Randomized, 24-week, Parallel-group, Non-inferiority, Open-label Active Controlled Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of QVM149 With a Free Triple Combination of Salmeterol/Fluticasone + Tiotropium in Patients With Uncontrolled Asthma</official_title>
