  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to demonstrate that the efficacy of two treatment arms of the
      fixed-dose combination product QVM149 is non-inferior to the efficacy of the free combination
      arm of salmeterol/ fluticasone+ tiotropium in uncontrolled asthmatics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
